'''Kayonza''' ni akarere kamwe muri turindwi (7) tugize intara y'iburasirazuba ,gafite [[ubuso]]  bwa 1,935Km2,Gatuwe n'abaturage bagera kuri 344,157 (ibarura rusange ry'abaturage 2012)<ref>http://www.kayonza.gov.rw/index.php?id=83</ref>

Akarere ka Kayonza kazi cyane mu kugira [[ibyanya nyaburanga,]] [[Umusozi|imisozi]], [[Ikiyaga cya Muhazi|ibiyaga]], [[amashuri]] menshi, [[ibiranga amateka]].

